   EXPLANATION
  	the action tag has 1 compulsory fields namely name. Action name is free to choose but I recommend to use the current file names.
  	implementation field will correspond to the generic or subclass
  	Maximum parameters is the max number of parameters SlashAction passes
  	Minimum parameters is the min number of parameters SlashAction passes (usually 0)
  	Action type is the type: can be invisible, addbuddy, etc. 
  	putAction are optional fields. These fields can contain the additional action parameter names, like target, etc.
  	The actual parameter values will come from the SlashAction interface
  	
  	
  	  <action name="echo action">
  	<implementation class-name="games.stendhal.client.actions.XMLSlashAction"/>
  	<MaximumParameters>2</MaximumParameters>
  	<MinimumParameters>0</MinimumParameters>
  	<type>echo</type>
  </action>
 
